= MODULE

sudo 

= DESCRIPTION

This is the sudo module, adapted from the module proposed by
camptocamp[https://github.com/camptocamp/puppet-sudo].
Configure and manage sudo and sudoers files

== Supported Platforms

* Debian
* Redhat and others: not  tested yet)

